| Purpose           | Library                                               |
| ----------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| UI                | Streamlit                                        |
| Speech Input      | SpeechRecognition + PyAudio                       |
| Speech Output     | pyttsx3                                           |
| AI Response       | transformers (offline) or OpenAI API (online) |
| Time/Date Parsing | dateparser                                        |
| Scheduling        | google-api-python-client                         |
| Data Storage      | pandas (CSV) or sqlite3                       |
